    "an7.618-644:0.2": "11. Abbreviated Texts Beginning With Greed ",
    "an7.618-644:0.3": "Untitled Discourses on Greed ",
    "an7.618-644:1.1": "“For the complete understanding of greed … ",
    "an7.618-644:1.2": "complete ending … ",
